					TriggerCooldowns = { "ZagreusBoonPickUpSpeech" },
					Text = "My daughter to a baseborn farm-boy, she... why, little sprout, I wasn't very kind to her, I think. Certainly not once her father passed. It was her mortal blood that made her weak! Born to mortals, taken by mortals, I suspect. So now, they {#DialogueItalicFormat}pay{#PreviousFormat}." },
